@startuml DesktopAuthFlow
title METRIC - Autenticação Desktop (Modo Free - SRS 4.1)
actor User
participant DesktopApp
participant ControlPlane
participant EmailService

User -> DesktopApp: Inicia App (sem login)
DesktopApp -> DesktopApp: Modo Free disponível
alt Usuário deseja Pro/Enterprise
    User -> DesktopApp: Solicita Login (Email)
    DesktopApp -> ControlPlane: POST /auth/magic-link {email}
    ControlPlane -> EmailService: Enviar Magic Link
    EmailService -> User: Recebe Email
    User -> DesktopApp: Clica no Link
    DesktopApp -> ControlPlane: Validar Token
    ControlPlane -> DesktopApp: JWT + User Profile + Organizações
    DesktopApp -> User: Acesso Liberado (Pro)
else Modo Free
    DesktopApp -> User: Usa sem autenticação
end
@enduml
